<section class="about-section">
  <div class="about-title">
    <h2><span class="about-black">About</span> <span class="about-accent">me</span></h2>
  </div>

  <div class="about-grid">
    <div class="about-image">
      <div class="about-image__inner">
        <img src="/profile.jpg" alt="Profile" width="400" height="750" />
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="about-text">
      <div class="about-text__inner">
        <p class="about-paragraph">
          I am a developer with three years of experience split between fast-paced company environments and custom freelance projects. Fueled by a lifelong obsession with The Matrix, I look at software through a sharp, analytical lens.
        </p>
        <p class="about-paragraph">
          Rather than fighting the rise of AI, I embrace it pragmatically to build faster and smarter. I am the creator of the <strong>Monolith Minimalism</strong> design philosophy, translating raw architectural weight into digital interfaces. My latest release is <a href="https://qiko-space.chat" class="about-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Qiko</a>, a decentralized P2P browser chat extension built for modern peer-to-peer communication.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-section {
    padding-top: 12.5rem;
    padding-bottom: 10rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 10rem;
  }

  .about-title {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: end;
  }

  .about-title h2 {
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .about-black {
    color: var(--nord0);
  }

  .about-accent {
    color: var(--nord8);
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: stretch;
  }

  .about-image {
    display: flex;
  }

  .about-image__inner {
    flex: 1;
  }

  .about-image__inner img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    display: block;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .about-text {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .about-text__inner {
    flex: 1;
    padding-left: 4rem;
    padding-right: 1rem;
    text-align: right;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: end;
  }

  .about-paragraph {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    color: var(--nord0);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .about-link {
    color: var(--nord8);
    text-decoration: underline;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .about-link:hover {
    color: var(--nord9);
  }
</style>
